### Functors

An abstraction that allows us to represent sequences of operations within a context such as a List, an Option, or any one of a thousand other possibilities.

Informally, a functor is anything with a `map` method.

![imageFunctor](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)


### Monads

Informally, a monad is anything with a constructor and a flatMap method. All functors 
are also monads, including Option, List, and Future.

![imageMonad](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)
